WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.333 --> 00:00:02.666
Enough is enough

2
00:00:02.666 --> 00:00:04.500
I said no no no no

3
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:16.600
Mom, what's wrong with you?

4
00:00:20.266 --> 00:00:22.100
Zhang Yi, what did you tell my mother?

5
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:23.500
Why did you hurt my mother?

6
00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:24.466
Didn't you say

7
00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:25.933
Everything you have now

8
00:00:25.933 --> 00:00:27.200
I gave it to you

9
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.866
You have to follow my instructions

10
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:30.166
Why?

11
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:32.600
Why can you limit our personal freedom?

12
00:00:32.933 --> 00:00:34.733
I'm taking my mom back to grandma's tomorrow

13
00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:36.933
Xiaoya, do whatever you want

14
00:00:36.933 --> 00:00:38.433
I sometimes really want to stay

15
00:00:38.766 --> 00:00:40.400
If you dare to hurt my daughter

16
00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:41.500
I'll fight with you

17
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.066
What right do you have to talk to me like this?

18
00:00:43.066 --> 00:00:44.933
Did you forget that I am your wife?

19
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:46.500
You take yourself too seriously.

20
00:00:46.500 --> 00:00:47.466
I tell you the truth

21
00:00:47.466 --> 00:00:48.300
In my eyes, Jiang Yin

22
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:50.000
You are nothing more than a dog

23
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:53.966
I married you because I love you

24
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:55.566
If you talk to me like that

25
00:00:55.566 --> 00:00:57.666
I'm leaving here tomorrow with my daughter

26
00:01:08.700 --> 00:01:10.133
Han Yun, sorry

27
00:01:10.133 --> 00:01:12.266
I just had a drink and there's nothing more to say

28
00:01:12.766 --> 00:01:14.900
I'm just so used to being in control

29
00:01:14.900 --> 00:01:16.433
You forgive me

30
00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:18.900
Han Yun

31
00:01:19.533 --> 00:01:20.800
I am worse than pigs and dogs

32
00:01:20.966 --> 00:01:23.066
I don't know how to cherish such a good wife

33
00:01:23.166 --> 00:01:24.500
If you don't forgive me

34
00:01:24.500 --> 00:01:25.566
I just kept hitting myself.

